comments: Curry (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Holiday's (MIL) path and absorbs the contact.
Johnson (BKN) is already in Holiday's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs as he releases from the contact.
Holiday (MIL) steps slightly forward towards Curry (BKN) and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Johnson (BKN) is already in Holiday's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Johnson (BKN) steps slightly forward towards Antetokounmpo (MIL) and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Johnson (BKN) places his hand to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) side and immediately slides his hand off as he defends the shot attempt.
Matthews (MIL) is moving alongside Irving's (BKN) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly grasps Drummond's (BKN) jersey and marginal contact occurs as he deflects the ball during rebounding.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes his left foot as his pivot foot and he maintains his pivot foot after his gather.
Holiday (MIL) is the first player to touch the ball in the backcourt, and a backcourt violation is correctly called.
Matthews (MIL) legally contest Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Irving (BKN) brings his arm forward towards Antetokounmpo (MIL) and marginal body contact occurs as Drummond (BKN) simultaneously blocks the shot.
Matthews (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Drummond's (BKN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Johnson (BKN) cleanly blocks Portis' (MIL) jump shot attempt.  Any ensuing arm contact is marginal.
Portis (MIL) commits a take foul on Drummond (BKN).
Portis (MIL) hands off the ball in Irving's (BKN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Irving (BKN) moves forward into Allen's (MIL) body and initiates contact during his jump shot attempt.
Mills (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Matthews' (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Aldridge (BKN) and Middleton (MIL) briefly engage during the inbound and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) moves towards Aldridge (BKN) and marginal contact occurs after Aldridge has released his pass.
Carter (MIL) commits a take foul on Irving (BKN).
Curry (BKN) and Middleton (MIL) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Curry (BKN) reaches across Middleton's (MIL) front and initiates contact prior to the start of Middleton's upward shooting motion.
Aldridge (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Holiday (MIL) and he absorbs the contact.
Mills (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Matthews' (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Holiday (MIL) commits a take foul on Irving (BKN).
Johnson (BKN) commits a take foul on Holiday (MIL).
Carter (MIL) briefly places his hand to Curry's (BKN) side after the pick and slides his hand off as he rolls toward the baseline.
Holiday (MIL) commits a take foul on Irving (BKN).
Johnson (BKN) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Ibaka (MIL) commits a take foul on Aldridge (BKN).
